  annote =       "Uses the Torrance- Sparrow (see [Blinn 77]) hypothesis
                 to propose an improved reflection model. The model
                 computes the spectral energy distribution of light
                 reflected from a surface. Geometric surface
                 characterestics such as surface roughness, microfacet
                 slope and microfacet orientation were modelled on a
                 statistical basis and used to predict both the spatial
                 and spectral distribution of the reflected light.
